ength    = 19:33\n\n| title1          = Bad Boy for Life\n| writer1         = Wesley, Curry, Ross, Fisher, Goss\n| length1         = 4:09\n\n| title2          = Bad Boy for Life\n| note2           = instrumental\n| writer2         = Wesley, Curry, Ross, Fisher, Goss\n| length2         = 4:09\n\n| title3          = Let's Get It\n| note3           = remix\n| writer3         = Coleman, Graham, Ross, Green, Hodge\n| length3         = 5:19\n\n| title4          = Bad Boy for Life\n| note4           = music video\n| writer4         = Wesley, Curry, Ross, Fisher, Goss\n| length4         = 5:56\n}}\n\n==Credits and samples==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n;\"Bad Boy for Life\"\n*Performed by P. Diddy, Black Rob and Mark Curry\n*Produced by Megahertz Music Group\n*Vocal production by Harve \"Joe Hooker\" Pierre\n;\"Let's Get It\"\n*Performed by Three The... featuring [[G. Dep]], P. Diddy and Black Rob\n*Produced by Yogi\n*Additional production by [[Mario Winans|Mario \"Yellow Man\" Winans]]\n*Vocal production by Harve \"Joe Hooker\" Pierre\n*Contains excerpts of \"Love & Happiness\" by [[Al Green]]\n{{col-2}}\n;\"Let's Get It\" (remix)\n*Performed by Three The... featuring Kain, Mark Curry, [[Loon (rapper)|Loon]], G. Dep, P. Diddy and Black Rob\n;\"Can't Believe\"\n*Performed by [[Faith Evans]] featuring [[Carl Thomas (singer)|Carl Thomas]]\n*Produced by Sean \"P. Diddy\" Combs and Mario \"Yellow Man\" Winans\n*Contains excerpts from \"Phone Tap\" by [[The Firm (hip hop group)|The Firm]]\n;\"Hoodfellaz\"\n*Performed by The Hoodfellaz\n*Produced by Yogi\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Chart performance==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Chart (2001\u201302)\n!Peak<br>position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Australia|20|artist=P. Diddy, Black Rob & Mark Curry|song=Bad Boy for Life}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Austria|41|artist=P. Diddy, Black Rob & Mark Curry|song=Bad Boy for Life}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Flanders|14|artist=P. Diddy, Black Rob & Mark Curry|song=Bad Boy for Life}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Wallonia|7|art